dateheader version 1.0
==============================

Exports a tied scalar called $dateheader into the caller's
namespace.  This scalar, when stringified, gives a
RFC2822-compliant "Date:" header.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires perl 5.

